## AI Stack

- **Google GenAI** (primary LLM)
- **OpenAI** and **Anthropic** (fallback / specialized tasks)
- All configured per creator via `creator_config/[slug].json`

---

## Database

PostgreSQL via `psycopg2`. All schema and queries live in `app/storage/postgres.py`. **Never add new logic there** — only append migrations to existing tuples. See file-organisation rule.

---

## Scripts and Cron

- `scripts/` — one-off ingestion, backfill, and tooling scripts (~61 files)
- `operator/railway.*.toml` — scheduled cron jobs (Railway-managed, touch prod DBs)
- `tests/` — pytest suite (~38 modules)

---

## Logging (Railway)

Log lines are prefixed by service area for easy filtering:
- `[ZARNA]` — brain, messaging, live shows
- `[ADMIN]` — admin dashboard
- `[DB]` — storage layer
- `[SMB]` — SMB portal
- `[STATS]` — analytics
- `[WEB]` — everything else
